I think I scared the FedEx guy when he handed me this!!😳
.
.
.
Another perk of working with this incredible company...PERKS like this!! Rodan + Fields just sent me this FREE MacBook Air 👩🏼‍💻 and thanked me for LEADING THE WAY! 🤩
.
.
.
Never in my wildest dreams would I have believed that I would be the CEO of my own business! Never. But here I am #killingit and I’d love to have YOU along for the ride! 👯‍♀️
.
.
.
I mean the PERKS are endless! They love spoiling their consultants with APPLE products, lavish gifts and luxury trips...and this is only the beginning! I haven’t even been in the biz for 3 years.....imagine my 5 year and 10 year anniversary with this incredible company?! 🤯
.
.
.
So my friend....if you’re considering this for yourself...GO FOR IT! 🏃‍♀️I was scared. I wasn’t sure if I’d be good at it. I thought I was too busy. I thought I was above a business like this. I thought it was saturated. Blah blah blah. But the truth is anyone can do this business, ANYONE! You just have to believe in yourself and jump feet first!😉
.
.
.
